******
About:
******
In the space of a few years, Drax Project has grown from being music students busking on the streets (Drums + Sax) into one of the most watched groups to come out of New Zealand. Building on Wellington's tradition of killer live acts, Drax Project have honed their music as much on stage as in the studio. Beyond releasing several buzz singles on Universal and opening for acts like Ed Sheeran, Gorillaz Soundsystem, Brian McKnight, Camila Cabello & Lorde, the boys have just released their EP NOON on 300. 

*****

*****
 Shaan Singh - Saxophone | Lead Vocals | Synth
